                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18280221-195-off1036 t18280221-195-crimeloc1039"></join>. On the 22d of January I was in the parlour, and heard footsteps - I ran out, and was directed up the street, but could not find any one; and while I was telling the watchman the prisoner came by the shop, with this bacon under his arm, and was taken - he did not say how he got it.</p>
               <p>
            
